%body{style: "background-color: #fff; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"}
  %table{style: "background-color: #F2F5F9; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"}
    %tr
      %td{style: "padding: 40px;"}
        %h1{style: "font-size: 32px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: center;"}
          Welcome to Wrapt
          %sup{style: "margin-left: -2px;"}
            &#8482;
        -# %p= "Dear #{@profile.name},"

        %p{style: "text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #C5AA80; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75;"}
          #{@profile.owner.first_name || 'Someone'} has been shopping for gifts for you on Wrapt
          =succeed ', ' do
            %sup
              &#8482;
          %br
          a new gift-giving site dedicated to better gifting with artisanal items, memorable experiences and funds for your wish-lists in life.

        %p{style: "text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #444; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.75;"}
          #{@profile.owner.first_name || 'They'}, together with curators from Wrapt
          =succeed ', ' do
            %sup
              &#8482;
          chose gifts for you based on answers they gave to a short quiz regarding your personality, passions and purpose.

        %p{style: "text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #444; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.75;"}
          He (as well as we!) would love to know what you think about these gifts he chose. 
          %br
          Would you review and mark as liked/not liked for the reasons in the pull down menu? 
        %p{style: "text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #444; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.75;"}
          Given that this is our testing period before our actual launch, your feedback is super-helpful and appreciated.
        
        

        = link_to "See what #{@profile.owner.first_name || 'he'} picked out for you", profile_recipient_review_url(@profile.recipient_access_token), style: "display: block; background-color: #ABBAD5; color: #333; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.4px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1;"
